What you need to know:  Beer brand has been the king of sports sponsorship in the region - boxing, football, rugby, darts et al, bringing fame and fortune to athletes and smiles to a whole nation  The story touches millions of people. It is a story worth telling. And as KBL Managing Director, John Musunga, said: “The history of Tusker is inextricably intertwined with that of Kenya as a nation. Its centenary milestone is testament to the resilience and grit of the Kenyan people, and a confirmation of the limitless possibilities we can achieve if we work together for a common goal – as encapsulated in Tusker’s “Pamoja Milele” philosophy.”